 +  and   3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x760d6ea16c00>([1, 4])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x760d6ea16c00> = [[1, 4], [1, 4, 1], [4], [4, 1], [1, 4], [1, 4, 1], ...].count
 +  and   2 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x760d6ea16c00>([4, 1])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x760d6ea16c00> = [[1, 4], [1, 4, 1], [4], [4, 1], [1, 4], [1, 4, 1], ...].count
